Package burp.api.montoya.ui.editor.extension

Interface ExtensionHttpRequestEditor

public interface ExtensionHttpRequestEditor
Extensions that register an HttpRequestEditorProvider must return an instance of this interface. Burp will then use that instance to create custom tabs within its HTTP request editor.
